<h1>Account and Data Deletion</h1>

<p>
This page explains how users can request deletion of their Breed Connect account
and associated personal data.
</p>

<hr>

<h2>How to Request Account Deletion</h2>

<p>
Users can request deletion of their Breed Connect account by sending an email to:
</p>

<p>
<strong>Email:</strong> antnodetechnologies@gmail.com
</p>

<p>
The email must be sent from the <strong>registered phone number or email address</strong>
associated with the Breed Connect account to allow identity verification.
</p>

<hr>

<h2>What Data Will Be Deleted</h2>

<p>
Upon successful verification, the following data will be permanently deleted:
</p>

<ul>
  <li>User account information</li>
  <li>Phone number and email address</li>
  <li>Animal records and breeding data</li>
  <li>Animal photos and uploaded images</li>
  <li>User-generated content and notes</li>
</ul>

<hr>

<h2>Deletion Timeline</h2>

<p>
Account and data deletion requests are processed within
<strong>7 working days</strong> after verification.
</p>

<p>
Some data may be retained if required to comply with applicable laws,
regulatory obligations, or legal enforcement requests.
</p>

<hr>

<h2>Contact</h2>

<p>
If you have any questions regarding account deletion or data handling,
please contact:
</p>

<p>
<strong>Email:</strong> antnodetechnologies@gmail.com<br>
<strong>App:</strong> Breed Connect<br>
<strong>Country:</strong> India
</p>

<hr>

<p>
By using Breed Connect, you acknowledge that the app is a private digital
management platform and that all user data deletion requests are handled
according to this policy.
</p>

